Author: lavendermyth
Text: Can you talk about this with her? My therapist and I fill out a new thing every year about what my goals are (been seeing her since 2012). If she's good at her job she'll listen and work with you to make changes about what you're focusing on and help you identify goals for therapy. If not, I'd find a new therapist.

Author: feelcrappeh
Text: I'd find a new one to be honest :/
